8 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to authorize the
9 Governor during a declared state of emergency to authorize the Agency of
10 Natural Resources to waive applicable water quality permits or requirements to
11 allow dams within the State to draw down water levels in anticipation of a
12 flood event likely to cause substantial damage or injury to persons or property.
